      "content": "k sounds good. but wait, i just saw the system log—it says the supplier is saying the shipment is delayed by at least 3 weeks. if we keep them 'in stock' and people keep ordering but we can't ship them, isn't that gonna mess up our fulfillment ratings and get us in trouble with the warehouse team? what's the play here?",
